date.headline: Nikon D800 Photos of Swimsuit Bikini Model Goddess reading Great Books!
date.text: Nikon D800 Photos of Swimsuit Bikini Model Goddess reading some of the official Great Books of 45SURF: Shakespeare's collected works, Homer's Iliad and Odyssey, and Moby Dick (My favorite American novel)! I was shooting some slow-motion 60p video at the exact same time as these photographic stills with a Panasonic X900MK camcorder bracketed to my Nikon D800--enjoy the goddess video: youtu.be/errPtr5aBrg www.youtube.com/watch?v=DMEzMwSbCqc Be sure to watch the video in full 1080p HD! She's an archetypal Hero's Journey Mythology Goddess for sure! Naussicaa from Homer's Odyssey perhaps? :) The Shakespeare was printed in the eighteenth century in London! Shot with the Nikon D800 and Nikon 70-200mm f/2.8G ED VR II AF-S Nikkor Zoom Lens. Modeling the new Hero's Journey Mythology Gold'N'Virtue Gold 45 Revolver Swimsuits on a sunny winter's day in Malibu! Captured in both RAW and JPEG. Check out the amazing detail in the full resolution photos! I was running out of CF & SD cards fast, as the files are huge! All the best on your EPIC hero's journey!

date.headline: Green Eyes! Pretty Brunette in Santa Monica! Nikon D800   70-200mm VR2 F/2.8 Nikkor Lens Photos
date.text: "Bicycle bicycle bicycle I want to ride my bicycle bicycle bicycle I want to ride my bicycle!" -Queen "Beauty will save the world." --Dostoyevsky Gorgeous goddess with beautiful green eyes on a classic beach cruiser bicycle wearing jeans and a black bikini top! Pretty Brunette with long, wavy/curly brown hair in Santa Monica! Nikon D800 70-200mm VR2 F/2.8 Nikkor Lens Photos. She was tall, thin, fit and athletic with amazing abs! Here's some epic HD video of the beautiful brunette goddess: www.youtube.com/watch?v=e3tMqlLpRf4 www.youtube.com/watch?v=Y4CXppMeNLM www.youtube.com/watch?v=WzuqR901mq4 Shot with the Nikon D800 and AF-S NIKKOR 70-200mm f/2.8G ED VR II Nikon Lens & B W 77mm Kaesemann Circular Polarizer with Multi-Resistant Coating! The f 2.8 rocks! :) The polarizer even on overcast days adds my signature touch, as it cuts down on the SB-700 Speedlight Flash glare too. Modeling some 45SURF shirts/hoodies and the favorite Gold'N'Virtue Gold 45 Revolver swimsuits. May the Hero's Journey Mythology Goddesses guide, inspire, and exalt ye along yer heroic artistic journey! Best wishes from Johnny Ranger McCoy! "Follow your bliss, and don't be afraid, and doors will open where there were none before. . . You must give up the life you planned in order to have the life that is waiting for you." -The Great Joseph Campbell 'Tis true!
